data.description: This 4 bed / 3 bath home is located in the established Sherwood subdivision and minutes to TTU, CRMC, and all the local hotspots Cookeville has to offer. The main level offers a semi-private kitchen with plenty of space to entertain, a focal point fireplace, 2 main level bedrooms, and main level primary with full ensuite. The lower level offers flexibility for additional bedrooms, an office, playroom and family room, including a full bath and access to an oversized attached garage and utility space. The newly installed rear porch is the perfect place to enjoy your privacy nestled in the mature trees. With some cosmetic updating, this house will be sure to check all the boxes!
